         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="zoor0207.translation"
              corresp="#zoor0207.transcription">
            <p> One (is) the God. Monument of your servant Claudius, who died having a good name
                    and good faith (at the age) of seventeen years, in the year 351 on (the) 17th
                    (day) of the month Artemisios, on (the) second day of the week (Monday). Be of
                    good cheer, no one (is) immortal. </p>
         </div>
